			"name": "Sunlight Vulnerability",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>At the start of each of its turns, if the vargheist is in direct sunlight, it becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} and takes @Damage[20[vitality]] damage. If the vargheist was already @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed}, it increases the condition by 1, and is destroyed when it becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 3} due to the sunlight.</p>",
